  <title>Samostalno prijavljivanje</title>

  <p>Možete da izmenite vaša podešavanja tako da budete samostalno prijavljeni na vaš nalog kada pokrenete vaš računar:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Otvorite <app>Podešavanja</app> iz pregleda <gui>Aktivnosti</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Otvorite panel <gui>Korisnici</gui> u <app>Podešavanjima</app>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Izaberite korisnički nalog na koji želite samostalno prijavljivanje prilikom pokretanja.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Pritisnite <gui style="button">Otključaj</gui> i unesite vašu lozinku.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Prebacite dugme <gui>Samostalno prijavljivanje</gui> na <gui>Uklj.</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p>When you next start up your computer, you will be logged in automatically.
  If you have this option enabled, you will not need to type in your password
  to log in to your account which means that if someone else starts up your
  computer, they will be able to access your account and your personal data
  including your files and browser history.</p>

  <note>
    <p>If your account type is <em>Standard</em>, you cannot change this
    setting. Contact your system administrator who can change this setting
    for you.</p>
  </note>

